00:00:32.320 --> 00:00:37.980
Gokart track is the place where most of professional drivers began their adventure with motosport.

00:00:38.220 --> 00:00:40.600
Karting is a sport for everyone.

00:00:40.860 --> 00:00:45.760
It is simple. If you want to race, leave the streets, come here and do it safe.

00:00:45.760 --> 00:00:50.740
